Today I went out fishing with the @runcl_official Titan 2 4000 reel, the @tzackfishing tzach classic 6-12 lb 7’2 fast action rod, and the @arcticspinners 5/16th oz firetiger and green body spinner! Within the first 5 minutes I had a monster northern pike strike and I lost it right at the net. But luckily I still hooked up on this other northern and got some amazing footage of some other great pike strikes! Stay tuned for the video coming out soon!

New video is up! Check it out to see how to fish small rivers for pike as well as how to easily night time fish the st clair river from shore for walleye!
@waterlandco @runcl_official @arcticspinners @thumpemsoftplastics @tzackfishing @justfishinapparel
Sofia had a fun day swimming in the pool 🏊‍♀️

I’d like to say a big thanks to @piscifun_official for sending me their Alijoz 8.1:1 right hand retrieve reel! I plan to be using this reel on my bass pro shops extra heavy musky rod to catch some giant muskies on! They also sent me the Chaos Xs 5.3:1 right hand retrieve reel. I plan on using this reel to catch walleye, laketrout, catfish, and sturgeon on this reel! I still have some more great products on their way to my house which should arrive any day and I can’t wait to receive them! Stay tuned to see these products in my future videos!
Sometimes it’s not always about the monster that you can reel in but about the happy smile that you can put on someone else’s face!

I’d like to say a big thanks to @piscifun_official for sending me their Carbon X 1000 ice fishing reel! This reel has 11 ball Bearings and only weighs 5.7 ounces! I can’t wait to go out icefishing after lake trout, steelhead, and Atlantic salmon with this reel!

I’d like to say a big thanks to @piscifun_official for sending me their two piece lumicat catfish casting rod!  Having a rod tip that lights up in the dark will be a game changer! This rod is rated up to 50lbs and I can’t wait to see the big fish I can land on this rod!
Happy 4th of July 🇺🇸 Sofia and I agree I officially need a hammock swing😁

I’d like to say a big thanks to @psychofishinglures for sending me one of their stylish hoodies as well as 2 packs of there tube jigs and 2 packs of their 3.8” rip rap plastics! I can’t wait to try these tube jigs out on some lake trout in December and to see what else I can catch on them till then!

Last night I went out fishing with the @piscifun_official lumicat fishing rod and the @piscifun_official chaos xs fishing reel and put the hurting on the fish! We caught a ton of walleye, sheepshead, silver bass, and rockbass! I will try and have the video posted on Sunday! Stay tuned to see what lures got the most bites and to see some great products in action!

I’d like to say a big thanks to @runcl_official for sending me their Ancohuma 2000 size reel to try! I’ll be putting this reel on my ultralight rod to do some creek fishing for northern pike and small mouth bass! Stay tuned to see this reel in my future videos!

Here’s a picture I forgot to post last year! The mosquitos have me missing winter fishing 🦟 This fish was landed on a @runcl_official Titan 2 4000 reel and a @diawafishinggear revros rod with a @acmetackle little Cleo!
Had a blast today playing paintball at kizzy field!
Had a fan today recognize me at the Fowlerville a and w today! She started jumping up and down with excitement so I couldn’t deny taking a photo with her! Thanks for watching my show molly!
Had a great season with these guys! It has been a ton of fun playing for the last five years. Last play off games are today to finish off the season strong!

Today I accomplished every anglers dream! Catching my new largest fish ever to date! This monster took 12 and a half minutes to battle from shore and is now my new personal best fish I have ever caught in fresh water and in saltwater! I have to give out a huge thanks to @piscifun_official for making such a great reel and giving it to me to see what I can catch on it. This reel helped me land my new largest fish ever!!!! The Alijoz reel 8:1:1 grey gold model is one of my favorite reels I have ever used… and it just landed me my largest fish ever… right after the battle and getting the fish back in the water I fell right on my back and layed down in awe… life Is good 🎣 😎 I was cradling this fish touching my chest… this was a absolute monster!!!!
I’m officially a new owner to a 16 foot star craft fishing boat 🎣 can’t wait to put a bunch of upgrades and extras on it and see what kind of fish I can catch!

FREE Guided SALMON and STEELHEAD Combo Fishing Trip Giveaway in south east Michigan! 

The Winner can choose any open day I have in January or February for ice fishing (if ice on date selected) or shore fishing combo trip for Atlantic Salmon, Steelhead, laketrout, and Coho Salmon!

Rods, reels, bait and tackle is all supplied. All necessary be fishing gear is supplied. You would just need your Michigan fishing license, polarized sunglasses, cold weather gear, cooler for your fish, food/drinks, and a pair of ice cleats if ice fishing. 

To be eligible to enter alls you have to do is follow “Cute Birds “The Fisher Brad Guide Service” on Facebook! 

To enter for 5 entries you just have to share the post! If you share it to a fishing group you’ll get an additional 5 shares! You can share the original post or any post that you see this in any fishing group! 

Each person you tag you will get an additional entry. You can make additional comments for one extra entry per tag. So if you make one comment with ten tagged people you will get 10 entries. If you make 10 seperate comments with 10 people tagged you will get 20 entries! 

I’ll be typing up names, cutting them up, and drawing a random lucky winner! 

Once confirmed the Winner was following the. Page it will be announced on January 18th at 9:00 pm! First date the winner could pick is January 19th! Video will be posted to “the fisher brad” YouTube channel.
